title: Captain America Hates Captain Marvel 【Marvel's Superheroes Parody】

json.text: Alright guys, I have an announcement to make.
We have a... new member in the team!!
Oh my gawd, this is it, I can’t believe I can finally meet her in person!
I don’t think my heart can take it, dude.
Let me introduce to you… the first female Marvel superhero to get her own solo movie.
Weighing in at 165 pounds, standing 5 ‘11” tall.
Carol Danvers is a half-human pilot, half-Kree...
...and said to be the most powerful Avenger to date.
Ladies and gentlemen, I give you…
CAPTAIN MARVEL !!!
What is up, Avengers.
Are we having fun tonight?
How about some fireworks to spice keep things going?
Captain! Captain! Captain! Captain! Captain! Captain!
As far as I concern, there is only ONE captain in this team.
And that is of course, yours truly.
Guys, if we stayed very still, they wouldn’t know we are here...
trust me, I do that all the time
That's enough!
Both of you!
Steve, I made you better than this.
Carol, I’m very disappointed in you.
But Jack, Stan, she started it! I was here first!
Nah ah! I was already busy saving the world from evil aliens, while YOU...
were still chilling in your ice cube.
I should be the captain! Not you!
How dare you came to MY headquarters and tell everyone that you can have MY captain title...
Are you kidding me ? I can't believe how the legendary captain America the head ...
like a 7-year-old child throwing a tantrum
CAROL DANVERS!!
STEVEN ROGERS!!
They used their full names…
Yo, there’s so much drama here, I’m loving it
That’s my boy and girl. Hahaha…
C’mon guys, where are the smiles?
Yup, Yup! Excelsior !!!
Thanks so much for watching and don't forget to subscribe and follow us on
Instagram and Facebook. Simply search Cartoon Hooligans .
Alright! See ya!
